 <summary>High-performance 128-bit identifier extension for PHP</summary>
 <description>A native PHP extension for working with 128-bit identifiers including UUIDs and ULIDs. Provides significant performance improvements over userland implementations with full RFC compliance, comprehensive encoding support, and deterministic testing capabilities.</description>
