 <license uri="https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT">MIT</license>
 <notes>
Initial release of the identifier extension.

Features:
- Complete UUID support (versions 1, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7)
- ULID support with Crockford Base32 encoding
- Comprehensive encoding support (Base32, Base58, Base64 variants)
- Context system for deterministic testing
- Automatic stub generation with rich documentation
- High-performance native C implementation
- Full RFC 4122 and RFC 9562 compliance
 </notes>
